commit_comments.body:
Interesting and if I take the CamleContext parameter out of the method CamelAutoConfiguration#camelBeanPostProcessor and instead add it as a class variable like this 

```
@Autowired
CamelContext camelContext;
```

Then my application starts up nicely! Thanks

